title: The Great Debate: Inmendham vs. à-bas-le-ciel.
description:
I think I can genuinely say that my original argument was "concise" (at 20 minutes), given that the response from Inmendham is closer to an hour and a half.
(Link 1:) The Meaning of Life: Against Anti-Natalism (Sam Harris, David Benatar, Inmendham) https://youtu.be/fwe4KUX5Spo
(Link 2:) Inmendham's riposte (an hour and a half long, and a LOT LESS COHERENT than this (edited) video you're watching now): https://youtu.be/sIC_pMiJa8Y
